snippet.title: RAW Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Kickstarter suspends our campaign. Here is the official reason: "Your project stated that, "After Kickstarter campaign, we will start Indiegogo campaign." This is against our rules and best practices".

We are preparing new campaign on Indiegogo.
Follow latest news on Discord: https://discord.gg/vsAAR5K

_____________________________________________

RAW is a new upcoming sandbox open world MMORPG with unique approach to social structure and high attention to gameplay details.

Sign up for our newsletter at http://killerwhalegames.com and get exclusive in-game bonus content!
